726743f-a.title: Queens: George Avenue - Cypress Avenue
726743f-a.text:
George Ave., vest side, north from Cypress Ave. (horse thereon) to
Seneca Ave., showing in the foreground, Ridgewood Grove. In the back-
ground is P.S. 77.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
